Poland cancels several payments for Ukrainian refugees.

According to the government website, from July 1 the following will be canceled:

- one-time payment of 300 zlotys for each refugee;

- payments under the “40+” program;

- accommodation and food in collective centers for refugees will be paid. Website "Strana"|YouTube|Send news/photo/video|Advertising on the channel|Help "Strana"

On April 10 at 15:00 (Moscow time) in the press center of the Izvestia International Research Center there will be a press conference dedicated to Cosmonautics Day celebrated on April 12.

Participants:

• Director of the Institute of Space Research RAS@mediaikiAnatoly Petrukovich;

• Director of the Institute of Medical and Biological Problems of the Russian Academy of Sciences@imbp_ruOleg Orlov;

• executive director and chairman of the organizing committee of the SIRIUS-23 experiment, head. Laboratory of Physiology of the Immune System, IBMP RANSergey Ponomarev;

• scientific director of the Institute of Astronomy RAS Boris Shustov;

• chief designer of the “Arctic” project, NPO named after. S. A. Lavochkina Anatoly Krainov. The broadcast will be available on the Izvestia MIC website. About media accreditation, follow the link.

Forwarded from: Naspravdi
